cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with privacy protection in street-view images using LiDAR data and detection algorithms. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is also likely as privacy is a major concern in this paper and the authors propose a system to protect sensitive information. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes a solution based on state-of-the-art deep learning detectors. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also possible as the paper deals with the performance of different detectors and proposes a faster and more accurate solution. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with street-view images and their processing.
